        <text><![CDATA[ <p> Designates June 6, 2008, as a national day of prayer and rededication for the men and women of the United States Armed Forces and their mission.</p> <p> Encourages Americans to join the Senate in such national day by reflecting on President Roosevelt's D-Day radio prayer.</p>]]></text>
